<subSubSection id="643BA2CABDD3A682BCCF86AA7FCF37E1" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="5A9E5C5AB311E421ECD7AD5D14937EB6" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C687836A996B893E185CF69F23194DBD" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">This species is known from the central-western coast of Madagascar (Boeny and Menabe regions).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="F911DDCD98A5C3CCB2A66E9DB28B0878" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" type="taxonomic remarks">
<paragraph id="719ED6B5239A179C6EA3D74669611EB0" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">Taxonomic remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A76C750902A8AA7B7ADC28C054FC3D73" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">
<bibRefCitation id="1326333762E09187A0C5DC9005F31056" author="Paulian, R" journalOrPublisher="Revue Francaise d'Entomologie" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" pagination="113 - 118" refId="B27" refString="Paulian, R, Cambefort, Y, 1991. Remarques sur le genre Helictopleurus et description de trois nouvelles especes (Coleoptera, Scarabaeidae). Revue Francaise d'Entomologie 13: 113 - 118" title="Remarques sur le genre Helictopleurus et description de trois nouvelles especes (Coleoptera, Scarabaeidae)." volume="13" year="1991">Paulian and Cambefort (1991)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName id="CC8B73579ADA422B76DC5219791C74CE" genus="H." lsidName="H. peyrierasi" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" rank="species" species="peyrierasi">
<emphasis id="7F6E4CEA8A8D768383E72CEBE02753F6" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">H. peyrierasi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from Zombitsy, south-western Madagascar. 
<bibRefCitation id="C3F68D5166E60EFB7ED46B2440A3788C" author="Montreuil, O" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" pagination="373 - 376" refId="B20" refString="Montreuil, O, 2005b. Contribution a l'etude du genre Helictopleurus d'Orbigny, 1915. Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France 110: 373 - 376" title="Contribution a l'etude du genre Helictopleurus d'Orbigny, 1915." volume="110" year="2005 b">Montreuil (2005b)</bibRefCitation>
, after having examined specimens collected in nearby Kirindy, and having compared them with the type specimens of 
<taxonomicName id="613EF42249B558E78C692480D61A3B3A" baseAuthorityName="Fairmaire" baseAuthorityYear="1899" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Helictopleurus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Helictopleurus fungicola" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fungicola">
<emphasis id="FD53B9AF9385B36A81EE24EBC7B44FE4" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">Helictopleurus fungicola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, treated this taxon as a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName id="CF22A46A6F232CEE6800F441C2234880" genus="H." lsidName="H. fungicola." pageId="0" pageNumber="63" rank="species" species="fungicola.">
<emphasis id="2BD3B69AF905A630E664154D981C7B3B" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">H. fungicola.</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
We compared the type specimens of the nominotypical subspecies with those of 
<taxonomicName id="F19651C88CF02A6C1BDBC9892E0B190D" genus="H." lsidName="H. fungicola subsp. peyrierasi" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" rank="subSpecies" species="fungicola" subSpecies="peyrierasi">
<emphasis id="3EF145C1DF3DAC2A01FB80B08B323322" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">H. fungicola peyrierasi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and found significant differences, especially in the shape of male genitalia, that support the original treatment of 
<taxonomicName id="C859A4DDC2A4EEBCD80453298F0D8A5F" genus="H." lsidName="H. peyrierasi" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" rank="species" species="peyrierasi">
<emphasis id="6A19EA03B2323D085C0D8C8CF3D55DB8" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">H. peyrierasi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
stat. rest. as a full species within the genus 
<taxonomicName id="B11F7E9127F8C17DD2847D015521C45C" authorityName="Orbigny" authorityYear="1915" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Helictopleurus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Helictopleurus" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="D34FB5F3F45C0600951EF5AD98B77663" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">Helictopleurus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
